quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  71,21,Noah dir My Lord ili disobeyed me sekv those est eben corrupted when ben mon infan
  71,22,Ili schemed terrible schemes
  71,23,Ili dir ne abandon your di! Ne abandon Wadd Suwaa Yaghouth Ya ooq Nasr
  71,24,Ili misled many Do let wicked plongx profund into loss
  71,25,Because da their pek ili dron asign hellfire. Ili ne trov helpers protekt them DI
  71,26,Noah ankaux dir My Lord ne las single disbeliever ter
  71,27,Se vi let them ili nur mislead your servants don nask al nothing wicked disbelievers
  71,28,My Lord forgive me my parents anyone enters my hejm as believer all kred hom women Ne don disbelievers anything annihilation